item.title: A Little Bit About Me
item.description: Prior to My Current Career First off, let us start with my name. I am Drake! No no, not the music artist, but a normal guy from the midwest that has a college degree in computer science that gave me the basic framework that I use everyday. Before college, I worked at a local grocery chain starting off stocking shelves working in various departments. This was a normal thing to do still at that age in my hometown.
